    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The ToolTreaux flat-file set is constructed of high-quality durable steel with a chrome finish, providing durability and resistance to rust and corrosion. They are diamond coated for extra strength, and each features a different grit size ranging from coarse to fine: 40, 80, 150, 240, 400, and 600 grit. Each file features a 2” PVC-dipped rubberized handle that will provide comfort, allowing for precision detail work. The non-slip grip will also help prevent injuries during use. Designed with durability in mind, the 6 different files are each 7” in length and have a 3/16” diameter. They are 3mm thick and are embedded on four sides for added strength. Diamond flat files are great tools for a number of projects due to their construction and strength</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Kidplokio Assorted Truck Toys Action Figures Lights Sounds Playset (2 Themes)</h2>\n  <p>Does your little one love trucks? Well, you’re in the right place! Kidplokio’s truck toy carrier play sets come in three themes: Construction, Dinosaur and Fire Truck. Whether it’s a firefighting mission, a construction site building adventure, or prehistoric playtime as a paleontologist, these awesome truck toys for boys are super fun!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>TOY TRUCKS:</strong> Available in construction tools or firefighting themes, Kidplokio’s truck toy carriers come with bright lights, cool sounds and fun hand tools and accessories; these toy trucks also feature built in handles so playtime adventures can be taken to go for play dates, appointments or travel</li>\n    <li><strong>LIGHTS AND SOUNDS:</strong> Bright lights and fun sounds are built into all the toy trucks for the ultimate playtime experience, making it more fun and realistic come playtime with friends and family, inspiring imagination and creativity</li>\n    <li><strong>SCREEN FREE PLAYTIME:</strong> Sparking curiosity and developing dexterity and hand eye coordination, little one’s will benefit from creative pretend play while they participate in tactile, screen free playtime</li>\n    <li><strong>DURABLE AND SAFE:</strong> All truck toys and accompanying accessories are safe for children ages 3 and up with adult supervision; Constructed of durable plastic that is easy to clean by wiping down and letting toys air dry</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Dimensions: 15 x 6 x 9 inches; Weight: 2.15lbs; Materials: Plastic; Warning: Choking Hazard, Small Parts; For Ages 3 and Up; Batteries Included</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/70201/undefinedKPL_dino_truck_car_carrier_parent.png\" alt=\"Does your little one love trucks\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> KPLFTRCK1</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Multi-Color</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Boasting lights, sounds and theme related action figures and accessories, kids will love creating their own pretend play adventures! All the themed truck toys feature lights and with the push of a few buttons, play sounds for the ultimate pretend play experience. Play pretend encourages creativity and imagination, while the tactile playtime experience helps children develop their fine motor skills and dexterity, while moving the action figures and vehicles around their play area. Hello screen free playtime!</p>\n  <p>Designed for at home or on the go play, these construction, dinosaur or fire truck toy play sets come with a convenient top carry handle, so little ones can bring their toys along with them on play dates, sleepovers, road trips, appointments and more. The truck toy carrier is easy to tote and travel with, as the sides snap closed, keeping action figures and accessories safety stowed.</p>\n  <p>All of the toys and accessories included with these toy truck play sets are safe for children ages three and up with adult supervision. And, made from durable materials, these toy trucks are designed to withstand all the action. For little guys who love construction or fire trucks, this a must have gift from Kidplokio! Collect them all!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "The ToolTreaux flat-file set is constructed of high-quality durable steel with a chrome finish, providing durability and resistance to rust and corrosion. They are diamond coated for extra strength, and each features a different grit size ranging from coarse to fine: 40, 80, 150, 240, 400, and 600 grit. Each file features a 2” PVC-dipped rubberized handle that will provide comfort, allowing for precision detail work. The non-slip grip will also help prevent injuries during use. Designed with durability in mind, the 6 different files are each 7” in length and have a 3/16” diameter. They are 3mm thick and are embedded on four sides for added strength. Diamond flat files are great tools for a number of projects due to their construction and strength.",
